# ============================================
# Spotify API Configuration
# ============================================
# 
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:
# 1. Go to https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard
# 2. Log in with your Spotify account
# 3. Click "Create App"
# 4. Fill in:
#    - App name: Dynamic Island (or any name)
#    - App description: Windows Spotify Controller
#    - Redirect URI: http://localhost:8888/callback
# 5. Click "Settings" to find your credentials
# 6. Copy this file to .env and fill in your values
#
# ⚠️ SECURITY WARNING:
# - NEVER commit .env to version control
# - NEVER share your Client Secret publicly
# - Rotate credentials if accidentally exposed
# ============================================

# Your Spotify Application Client ID (visible in dashboard)
SPOTIPY_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id_here

# Your Spotify Application Client Secret (click "View client secret")
SPOTIPY_CLIENT_SECRET=your_client_secret_here

# OAuth Redirect URI (must match exactly in Spotify Dashboard)
SPOTIPY_REDIRECT_URI=http://localhost:8888/callback
